mate-design-tri-fold -price-launch&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240700/huawei-mate-xt-ultimate-design-tri-fold-price-launch" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/10/24240700/huawei-mate-xt-ultimate-design-tri-fold-price-launch</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-10T04:06:52-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-10T04:06:52-04:00</updated><title> SpaceX 历史性的北极星黎明任务：如何观看发射</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一张显示 SpaceX 猎鹰 9 号火箭在 NASA 肯尼迪航天中心 39A 号发射场的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2woEiNTpON6Cbdptxnz0NtWiQLw=/0x38:6000x4038/ 1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73545449/2168615976.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;载人龙飞船太空舱将在 SpaceX 的猎鹰 9 号火箭上发射。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Joe Raedle / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tZ9AgH&quot;>;SpaceX 正准备出发其历史性的北极星黎明任务，该任务将利用其载人龙飞船将四名宇航员送入轨道。为期五天的穿越范艾伦辐射带的旅程将包括由私人宇航员完成的首次太空行走。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;wAOpgD&quot;>;如果您对这次任务感到好奇，以下是您应该了解的有关今天发射的信息定位当前定位为美国东部时间上午 5:23。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;bLhtHs&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; data-dnt=&quot;true&quot;align=&quot;center&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir =&quot;ltr&quot;>;观看猎鹰 9 号在多日发射 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/PolarisProgram?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;@PolarisProgram&lt;/a>; 的北极星黎明号机组人员的现场直播围绕地球运行的任务 &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/u1KqQx5AFr&quot;>;https://t.co/u1KqQx5AFr&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>;— SpaceX (@SpaceX) &lt;a href=&quot;https:// /twitter.com/SpaceX/status/1833358277805039800?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;2024 年 9 月 10 日&lt;/a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;twVyuS&quot;>;北极星黎明任务是什么？&lt; /h2>; &lt;p id=&quot;BwmRbO&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/2/15/22934797/jared-isaacman-spacex-polaris-program-q-and-a&quot; >;首次宣布于 2022 年&lt;/a>;，北极星黎明是由亿万富翁兼私人宇航员贾里德·艾萨克曼 (Jared Isaacman) 资助的一项任务。除了艾萨克曼之外，还有三...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/26/24228803/spacex-polaris-dawn-mission-launch-date -time-watch-live&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/26/24228803/spacex-polaris-dawn-mission-launch-date-time-watch-live" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/26/24228803/spacex-polaris-dawn-mission-launch-date-time-watch-live</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T21:28:04-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T21:28:04-04:00</updated><title>谷歌和司法部的广告技术之争都是为了控制</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片拼贴画中的木槌准备砸碎 Google Ads 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZUnLK4lvseOXdeYZopfXFrK6SFg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73575402/STK445_ADVERTISING_STK093_GOOGLE_D.0.jpg ” />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;kL6Zdq&quot;>;谷歌和美国司法部都认为对方对一件事想要太多：控制权。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;frjvlw&quot;>;“控制权是垄断者的决定性特征，”司法部律师朱莉娅·塔弗·伍德 (Julia Tarver Wood) 在联邦政府针对这家搜索巨头的第二次反垄断审判的开庭陈述中表示，该审判周一在亚历山大拉开帷幕。 ，弗吉尼亚。对于政府来说，谷歌对出版商在线销售广告空间的方式以及广告商如何购买广告空间的每一步都施加了过多的控制，从而导致了一个以牺牲几乎所有其他人为代价而使谷歌受益的系统。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot; c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;p49WYZ&quot;>;&lt;q>;“控制权是垄断者的定义特征”&lt;/q>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot; D0Hy0Q&quot;>;对于 Google 来说，政府正在通过让其在更多方面与竞争对手打交道来寻求对一家成功企业的控制权......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 9/9/24240386/google-doj-ad-tech-antitrust-审判-court-day-one&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240386/google-doj-ad-tech-antitrust-trial-court-day-one" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240386/google-doj-ad-tech-antitrust-trial-court-day-one</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T19:37:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T19:37:15-04:00</updated><title> JD Vance 最新的关于猫的错误是关于移民吃它们的奇怪错误信息</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;JD Vance 的图形照片拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ptdKNQWLdkBTlMuelJAhH9Mg0KU=/20x0:2021x1334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73575258/STK204_JD_VANCE_A.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Cc0cI8&quot;>;共和党副总统候选人 JD Vance — &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.pbs.org/newshour/politics/republican-senate-candidates -promote-replacement-theory&quot;>;关于移民“取代”美国人的阴谋论的直言不讳的支持者 - 现在正在传播有关海地移民在俄亥俄州斯普林菲尔德杀害家庭宠物和受保护野生动物的错误信息。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HnmYze&quot;>;“现在有报告显示，人们的宠物被不应该出现在这个国家的人绑架并吃掉，”万斯 &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com /JDVance/status/1833148904864465117&quot;>;周一发布在 X&lt;/a>; 上，呼应了周末右翼社交媒体上流传的未经证实的谣言。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;DtAZAO&quot;>;万斯引用的未命名“报告”很可能来自 Infowars 或《每日邮报》，两者都发表了来源稀少的帖子海地移民吃宠物和野生动物。这两篇出版物都引用了 Facebook 帖子，其中有人声称他们的邻居...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240338/haitian-migrants-cats -springfield-disinformation-jd-vance-elon-musk&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240338/haitian-migrants-cats-springfield-disinformation-jd-vance-elon-musk" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240338/haitian-migrants-cats-springfield-disinformation-jd-vance-elon-musk</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T18:00:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T18:00:54-04:00</updated><title>达斯·维德的配音詹姆斯·厄尔·琼斯去世，享年 93 岁</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;James Earl Jones 2015 年的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Po20x2izq8qJqIHblv4f3wIlQnE=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73575068/492713228.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Jemal Countess / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;XwIRPy&quot;>;James Earl Jones，幕后杰出演员达斯·维达 (Darth Vader) 的声音，已于 &lt;a href=&quot;https://deadline.com/2024/09/james-earl-jones-dead-1236082801/&quot;>;根据 &lt;em>;Deadline&lt;/em>; 去世，享年 93 岁&lt;/a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9rcy0j&quot;>;琼斯于 1931 年出生于密西西比州的阿卡布特拉。在克服了语言障碍后，琼斯继续了辉煌的演艺生涯，创作了数十部作品几十年来的戏剧、电视节目和电影。他在百老汇起步，于 1958 年在科特剧院（现称为詹姆斯·厄尔·琼斯剧院）主演&lt;em>;坎波贝洛的日出&lt;/em>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;jkh9fx&quot;>;然而，他的作品1977 年在第一部&lt;em>;星球大战&lt;/em>;中的角色给观众留下了巨大的印记，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/news/james-earl-jones-dies-age -93-actor-darth-vader/#:~:text=琼斯%20请求%20his%20name%20not%20appear%20in%20the%20credits%2C%20out%20of%20deference%20to%20Prowse.%20[琼斯% 20would%20not%20be%20credited%20as%20the%20voice%20of%20Vader%20until%20the%20release%20of%20%22Return%20of%20the%20Jedi。%22]&quot;>;他最初并未被记入&lt;/a >; 出于对穿着达斯·维达套装的大卫·普劳斯的礼貌而为反派配音。虽然琼斯以其独特的声音而闻名&lt;em>;S...&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/ 24240301/james-earl-jones-darth-vader-voice-died&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240301/james-earl-jones-darth-vader-voice-died" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240301/james-earl-jones-darth-vader-voice-died</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T17:35:45-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T17:35:45-04:00</updated><title>您可以在此处预订 AirPods 4 和更新版 AirPods Max</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple AirPods 4 从包装盒中取出的特写图片，背景为灰色。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TPE_2I1YQ6pC9KpJoihu-rwICaE=/0x1:1463x976/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574984/AirPods_4_Press_Image.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 现在销售四款不同的 AirPods，全部支持 USB-C 充电。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Qah8ya&quot;>;与新的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on -apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;iPhone 16&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236958/apple-watch-series-10-hands-on-bigger-brighter- and-thinner&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10&lt;/a>;，苹果在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple-iphone 期间发布了 AirPods 的三个新版本-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;周一“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动&lt;/a>;。其中包括新款入门级 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/23313529/apple-airpods-4-noise-cancellation-price-features&quot;>;AirPods 4&lt;/a >; 售价 129 美元，购买高端 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239947/apple-airpods-4-hands-on-preview-features-anc&quot;>;AirPods 4具有主动降噪功能&lt;/a>;（ANC），售价 179 美元，以及修订后的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/airpods-max-second-gen-price -specs-features-release-date&quot;>;AirPods Max&lt;/a>; 售价 549 美元。这三款产品将于 9 月 20 日上市，今天即可预订。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;mzeW3e&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component =&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;AirPods Pro 2 很快将兼作助听器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2024/9/9/24236881/apple-airpods-pro-second-gen-hearing-aid-protection-features-update&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最重大的公告&quot;,&quot; url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;} ]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Z05s5J&quot;>;根据 Apple 的说法，两款新的 AirPods 4 型号的音质比 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/22744686/apple-airpods-third-gen-review&quot;>;第三代&lt;/a>;。它们还具有新功能，例如切换到 USB-C。 ANC 版本还在缩小的充电盒中内置了扬声器，使 Apple 的“查找我的”追踪器更加有效，并且无线充电可与 Qi 和 Apple 兼容...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T17:02:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T17:02:26-04:00</updated><title>在哪里预订 Apple Watch Series 10 和黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;多个不同颜色的 Apple 智能手表。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HKmtwHXNrsfefIy_OvKyUcXT9dE=/299x0:3541x2161/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574917/Apple_Watch_Series_10_lineup_240909.0. .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 更新了其产品阵容，添加了新的颜色和功能，包括睡眠呼吸暂停警报。&lt;/em>; |图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;iHg5y0&quot;>;iPhone 16 在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple 期间成为焦点-iphone-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;苹果公司周一举行的“It&#39;s Glowtime”活动&lt;/a>;，但这并不是唯一首次亮相的新产品。 Apple 还推出了全新 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;Apple Watch 系列10&lt;/a>; 以及现有 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239740/apple-watch-ultra-specs-price-features-release-date 的黑色版本&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2&lt;/a>;。两款产品均从今天开始接受预订，并于 9 月 20 日推出，Series 10 起价为 399 美元，最新的 Ultra 2 起价为 799 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>; &lt;aside id=&quot;CNtfva&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的 iPhone 16 活动：8 个最重大的公告&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239739/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-watch-series-10-airpods&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 发布带有噪音的 AirPods 4取消和更好的声音&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/23313529/apple-airpods-4-noise-cancellation-price-features&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;: “您可以在这里预订 AirPods 4 和更新的 AirPods Max”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/24240101/apple-airpods-4-max-headphones-preorder-buy-price-release- date&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;kMZYJC&quot;>;Apple Watch Series 10 是 Apple 最薄的可穿戴设备，配备全新广角 OLED 屏幕，迄今为止，苹果在智能手表中使用的最大显示屏。这款新型可穿戴设备在 Apple 的 S10 SiP（系统级封装）上运行，并具有许多新功能，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep- apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2&quot;>;包括睡眠呼吸暂停警报&lt;/a>;，这是一种人们停止呼吸的情况...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24236673/apple-watch-series-10-black-ultra-2-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:58:24-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:58:24-04:00</updated><title> iOS 18 将于下周发布，提供自定义主屏幕的新方法</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手持 iPhone 15 Plus。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WNgG5XEYRWmOIjLF9STcPvWDg_c=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574893/236791_Apple_iPhone_15_and_15_Plus_review _DSeifert_0006.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jUc5nn&quot;>;Apple 公布了 iOS 18 的发布日期，距离发布仅几天时间。该更新将于 9 月 16 日发布，将添加自定义 iPhone 主屏幕和锁定屏幕的新方法。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;UMjeYT&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 6/10/24172132/apple-ios-18-new-features-ai&quot;>;在 iOS 18&lt;/a>; 中，您可以自由&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24196806/ios-18 -android-chaos&quot;>;在主屏幕上重新排列应用程序和小部件&lt;/a>;并更改其外观。 Apple 还推出了重新设计的控制中心，以及&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/14/24178564/apple-password-managers-lastpass-sherlock&quot;>;新密码管理应用程序&lt;/a>;并支持&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24175479/ios-18-satellite-imessage-wwdc-2024&quot;>;卫星消息传送&lt;/a >;。其他一些更新包括消息中的新文本效果、改进的照片应用程序以及在邮件应用程序中整理收件箱的新方法。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;WLq0tJ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple Intelligence 及其（稍微）更智能的初探Siri&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/31/24209910/apple-intelligence-ios-18-preview-siri&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;iPhone 16 Pro 和16 Pro Max上手：别叫它快门按钮&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos- features-price&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;imuT4Q&quot;>;但是，此更新不包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/7/31/24209910/apple-intelligence-ios-18-preview-siri&quot;>;Apple Intelligence 功能&lt;/a>;即将应用于 iPhone 15 Pro 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/24237017/iphone-16-specs-features-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;整个 iPhone 16 系列&lt;/a>;。即将推出的工具将帮助您重写和总结文本...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date -iphone-16&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date-iphone-16" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240230/ios-18-release-date-iphone-16</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:54:21-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:54:21-04:00</updated><title> AMD 放弃旗舰游戏 GPU——首先追逐人工智能</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zkqw6znZkR3CDoqYTx-4ppyHr_A=/13x0:2040x1351/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73574881/twarren_201116_4300_0014.0.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Tom Warren / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EUeIkB&quot;>;AMD 正在大声说出安静的部分：它现在优先考虑人工智能领先于游戏玩家旗舰 GPU 的芯片。该公司刚刚制定了一项新的业务战略，将把 RDNA 游戏图形和 CNDA 数据中心的工作合并成一个通用的“UDNA”，首先瞄准人工智能。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HhUvnD&quot;>;在对 &lt;em>;Tom&#39;s Hardware&lt;/em>; 的两次采访中（你肯定会&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/gpus /amd-deprioritizing-flagship-gaming-gpus-jack-hyunh-talks-new-strategy-for-gaming-market?utm_medium=social&amp;amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;amp;utm_campaign=socialflow&quot;>;想要&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tomshardware.com/pc-components/cpus/amd-announces-unified-udna-gpu-architecture-bringing-rdna-and-cdna-together-to-take-on-nvidias-cuda -ecosystem&quot;>;阅读两者&lt;/a>;），AMD 计算和图形主管 Jack Huynh 并不拐弯抹角。他解释说，对于游戏显卡，现在的目标是以较低的价格建立规模和市场份额，而不是“山中之王”旗舰 GPU，因为后者尚未说服足够多的买家将 Nvidia 抛在身后。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;YMdEaz&quot;>;这是第一次采访的关键段落：&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>; &lt;p id=&quot;IwgSvx&quot;>;汤姆的硬件：就价格而言，你有......&lt; /p>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240173/amd-udna-gpu-ai-gaming-rdna-cdna-jack-huynh &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240173/amd-udna-gpu-ai-gaming-rdna-cdna-jack-huynh" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240173/amd-udna-gpu-ai-gaming-rdna-cdna-jack-huynh</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T16:40:19-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T16:40:19-04:00</updated><title> Beats 的新款 iPhone 16 保护壳可与相机控制按钮配合使用</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Beats 的新款 iPhone 16 保护壳系列。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/migkKziSXxI8ihOyNgR43Izu6LU=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574850/beats1.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Beats 的新款 iPhone 16 保护壳内部采用超细纤维衬里，有四种颜色可供选择。&lt;/em>; |图片：Beats&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;0rKkF0&quot;>;Beats，Apple 的其他产品&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236804/airpods-max- Second-gen-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;耳机&lt;/a>;品牌刚刚发布了其首款专为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/设计的智能手机保护壳系列9/9/24230103/iphone-16-pro-specs-features-price-release-date-apple&quot;>;Apple 16 系列&lt;/a>;，与新的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos-features-price&quot;>;相机控制按钮&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c -float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;NwH9tD&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;iPhone 16 Pro 和16 Pro Max上手：别叫它快门按钮&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24239802/iphone-16-pro-max-hands-on-apple-photos- features-price&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;KiCyz1&quot;>;售价 49 美元的硬壳聚碳酸酯保护壳具有“柔性侧壁”，有助于吸收跌落时的部分冲击力，并且超细纤维衬里可保护 iPhone 的表面。根据 Beats 的说法，每个外壳的外表面都经过“光滑的防刮涂层”处理，这一功能可能是为了解决苹果的问题 - 并且 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/9/9/24240167/apple-finewriting-cases-dead&quot;>;现已停产&lt;/a>; — &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/12/23863322/apple-watch -series-9-iphone-15-case-finewriting-fabric-leather&quot;>;微斜纹 FineWoven 手机壳&lt;/a>;，容易出现划痕。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;aqRWTh&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MCFU4LL/A/beats-iphone-16-pro-max-case-with-magsafe -sunset-purple&quot;>;今天可通过 Apple 网站订购&lt;/a>;，有午夜黑、山顶石、激流蓝和日落紫配色，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240190/beats-apple-iphone-16-pro-max-cases-camera-control&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240190/beats-apple-iphone-16-pro-max-cases-camera-control" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240190/beats-apple-iphone-16-pro-max-cases-camera-control</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry></feed>